Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:06.96,PZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(488,0)\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\b1\bord5\blur3\fs80\fsp10\c&H903D08&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(960,860)\3a&H29&}西之少年与青岚的骑士
